channel.title: ENSO-RS || High Quality Content [Real 667] RS2011 SIMULATION
channel.description:
[B]Enso - High Quality 2011 RuneScape [/B] [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/3536x6d.png[/img] [B]Server Details[/B] Enso's protocol version: 667. Cache version: 667. (Real cache) Networking: netty-3.2.6 (final)
[B]Developers[/B] Fuzen Seth Josh Loveandpower
[B]What we aim with Enso?[/B] To create a unique and mind-blowing 2011 RSPS, I have always loved the 2011 RuneScape and I enjoy work to with Enso. Enso will be having high amount of content and probably players aswell, in the future.
[B] Update Logs [/B] [B][27.9.2013 Part 2][/B] [B]-Added Sagaie [/B](Ranged weapon) -Fixed equipment bug; will open equipment stats interface without any glitches. Also closing is fixed you can access to tabs after it. -Cleaned out some world-bugs. -Added 5 new achievements.
[27.9.2013] -Started real RS 100% Start system. -Identified Dungeoneering foods; I'm working on with real Dungeoneering. -Added 100% Musician rest with configs and real musician restore speeds. -Posted new media.
[26.9.2013] -Added report abuse system. -Added blackmark system. -Added security system. -Added dupe detector.
Added optional home locations; Players can choose a home they want. The main home would be the centre of Grand Exchange. There is currently 5 homes to choose if you want to, home can be changed by speaking to Father Aereck. I have posted new media about this update. -Bug fixes was done.
[25.9.2013] -Added great dungeon system it's nice to use. -Added triangle areas to area system. (loads area data from .xml) -Added Al-Kharid desert. -Corrected magic combat; unfinished though but will be done in this week. -Fixed bugs on alching, cannot be used upon duel, random events and such. -Fixed Teleportation crystal saving locations; You cannot save to everywhere such a place where you have active controller. -Created shop for achievements which can be opened from the Noticeboard -tab.
[19.9.2013] -Added more content to Port Phasmatys. -Added item emptying. -Finished fillables, potions, vials and such. -Added magic on item packet. -Added alching spell. (fully finished) -Duellist caps are added and full system. -Flax picking, proper. -Improved the Enso's quest system.
[14.9.2013] -Added lootshare. -Added full Karamja dungeon. -Fixed ranging projectiles they're real now.
[13.9.2013] -Added some new lunar spells. -Overloads cannot be used in the duel arena session. -Marker seeds are not plantable in duel arena session. -Non-dwarf cannon safe spots are added, you cannot add cannon to godwars, random events and such. -Added proper teleportation crystal. -Implemented tasks programme to 'My Character' in task tab which is replaced as a noticeboard. -Added item bonus actions system and added with it hati paws and head XP bonus. -Added duellist caps, can be taken from same place as RuneScape, duel arena Estocada. -Full 'Milestone cape' -system. Example: Player reaches 100 total you will be receiving Milestone cape (10); this will automaticly appear in player's bank and message will be given. -Improved combat system -Improved Magic spell handling. -Fixed 5-6 bugs which was effective gameplay bugs. -Improved character statistics, it will also give information to player if hes currently muted.
[7.9.2013] -Improved woodcutting skill. -Added statistics in the task tab. (can be accessed from the dialogue) -Finished Dicing. [5.9.2013] -Added full pack-yak with banking items. This is useful specially at places such as revenants cave. -Added a big bunch more of summoning pouches and summoning familiars. -Improved Dwarf's Multicannon, also if it decay or a player loses it you have ability to get it back. -Improved combat system timers once again. -Added 20+ new achievements. -Leech prayers actually drains now stats of your opponent.
[2.9.2013] -More achievements was done. -Bugs of 'frog event' was patched.
[1.9.2013] -Achievements system finished. -Created 30+ new achievements. -Added bird nests with opening them.
[30.8.2013] -Gem chances upon mining, I have been spending time a lot with the random event. -Fixed a massive bunch of bugs again, since 667's are very buggy. -Banana trees added. -Fishing spots added to Shilo village, you needed to complete Hoarfrost Depths -quest to enter there, otherwise you will be force-teleported in middle which has some agressive zombies. -Some effective progress was made to the group system which will be used in Dungoneering with it's real interfaces to make it even more flawless. -Added more eat-able foods. -Added Prayer renewal potions. -Fishing skill was heavily improved with many new fishes to catch. -Started drunken dwarf event.
[28.8.2013] -The 'Noticeboard' -tab is now way much easier to navigate with. -Josh Resigned the development team. -Started to build a panel to deskop-client. -Started legitmate dicing since cache is 667 the dice has it's options. -Added a dialogue to the Spirit tree which will manage all world-wide teleportations. Also the quick option 'Teleport' will instantly open the teleportation interface.
[24.8.2013] -Ring of Stone and other transformation items. -Started H.A.M Hideout -Fixed very big bunch of bugs, you cannot place dwarf cannons to godwars, random event areas and such. -Searchables. -Fillables.
[18.8.2013] World content: Buckets, vials and other fillables has been added. Also realized that the cache is 667 which means we got the dice-bag options, 100% dicing will be added soon. [17.8.2013] Been busy with IRL, going to get my lifes first house in the IRL. Turning to 18 at this month's last day. - Fuzen Seth Added frost dragon dungeon. Dwarfs multicannon fixes. Diango sells more items.
[16.8.2013] Keldagrim entrances are handled now. Added some spawns and such to make it nicer.
[15.8.2013] Started a new quest 'Wanted', player has ability to enter Keldagrim (the home of dwarfs). Players can have items such as dwarven rock cake and ability to recolour a whip and much more. Combat system fixes, new item added: Bolas. Finally started work on global ships system. This will unlocks ability to use the ships around world. Ship charter has been added fully. Fairy rings has been added fully.
[14.8.2013] Appearence fixes. Developers mode. Cutscene system fixes & addons. Players can obtain Ring of Kinship once you have travelled to Daemonheim after the first time. Player would need to speak with the Dungeoneering tutor to have it.
[12.8.2013] Canoes started. Miscellania Resources started. Fixes to starting system, it's pretty much non-glitch able. Fixes to Dwarfs multicannon. (Shows to all players and such a disappearing bugs does not occurs.) Implemented real 667 cache correctly. Female appearence fixed. Combat system high-quality improvements. Added grandpa Jack to teleport aswell, located in the river bewteen edge / grand exchange Added Zanaris entering real way. Also content will being made such as the puro-puro minigame. Quests board detects player's quest progress. [green = completed, red = not-started] Cutscene system improved. Added base for fullscreen cutscenes
